Mā te whakamahi i tenei tono, konei koe whakaae ki te whakakape me te whakaae ki ona ngā.

Ko te kaihanga o tenei tono e kore e hanga i tetahi pūtāhui e pā ana ki te kakato, tika, me te tika o te hanga raraunga. Tetahi mahi tangohia e koe ki runga ki te ngā mōhiohio kitea e koe i runga i tenei tono he tino i to koutou tūpono ake. Ko te kaihanga o tenei tono e kore e waiho matou tika mo tetahi parekura, me te/ranei pakaru i roto i te hononga ki te whakamahi o tenei tono.

Ko te kaihanga o tenei tono e kore e te reira\'t āta te homai e te whakamahi o ngā raraunga i hanga mā te whakamahi i tenei tono\'s ratonga. Ko ake te reira ki te kaiwhakamahi o tenei tono ki te whakatau i te whānuitanga o te tīkina i te whakamahinga o ngā raraunga tukuna ki te i tēnei taupānga\'s ratonga. Heoi, te whakamahi o tenei taupānga\'s ratonga e kore e whakaputa ke i tetahi copyrights ranei te whakamahi i te whakaaetanga o te tukuna raraunga.
